  "body": "The --disable-hooks doesn't work when doing an `helm upgrade`.\r\n It does work with a `helm upgrade --install` when actually doing an install.\r\n\r\nI tested the problem locally and was able to fix it with a simple line.\r\nIt seems that in the [client.go](../blob/master/pkg/helm/client.go#L133) file it's missing a `req.DisableHooks = h.opts.disableHooks` after line 133\r\n\r\nWithout this the setting is lost and is never sent to tiller.",
